divs: Sighting DetailsI was in my house about to go to bed and I was staring out of my window when the house started vibrating. I saw it over the trees in my neighbors yard. When i first saw it i thought it was a plane but then i noticed it didn't make any sound. When I first saw it it moved right over my house not making any sound and going in a straight line. When i saw it I didn't know how to react to it because i wasn't sure what it was at first. I lost sight of it when it flew past my house.
